description:
There's a sense of freedom that comes from a marriage that holds no secrets.
After admitting to his wife, Ava, a secret fantasy of seeing her have sex with another man, the two call upon a male escort to make the fantasy a reality. Knowing how much it pleases her husband about her sexual exploits, Siri sets her sights on a prospective sales client that swings by to look at a house she's selling. To keep their marriage exciting, Romi arranges a tryst with her co-worker, while her husband secretly watches. Sexual tensions explode when Richie invites his friend Xander over to spend one night with his wife.

